jobInfo.postDescription:
Position Requirements
- Passionate about building software applications
- Care about quality of code and final deliverables
- Excellent team player
- Proficient in Java 11 
- Solid Knowledge of Hibernate, HQL is a must. Jaspersoft Studio experience is a plus
- Strong understanding of SQL and ORM
- NoSQLdatabase experience is a plus
- Experience in building and using REST APIs
- Good Knowledge of JavaScript & CSS appreciated
- Understand security and performance concerns
- Good written and oral English abilities preferred

Key Responsibilities
- Develop complex B2B or B2C back-end applications for Industry leader companies
- Ensure high quality of code and deliverables
- Contribute to high efficiency of the project team
- Responsible for meeting milestone objectives
- Learn and apply new technologies

brandComInfo.introduce:
We're funded in Shanghai since 2004, as an international IT company, committed to developing customized solutions toward long-term benefits for our customers.
我们于2004年在上海成立，是一家国际化的公司，致力于为企业提供定制化的IT方案，我们的方案着眼于客户的长期利益。

Do you want to join a company with an open culture, and meet with talented & high efficiency colleague to quick response our customers' needs.
这儿你能享受到Open的外企文化，你能遇上智慧且做事高效的同事，一起携手共进，快速响应客户的需求。

Come and join us to experience our variety activities: weekly sports, monthly party, annual party, team building etc.
加入我们来体验各种丰富的公司活动：每周小运动，月度party，年度party，团建活动。。。

Come and work with interesting souls, trust me, you will get endless pleasure.
来和有趣的灵魂一起工作，收获无穷的乐趣。

We are waiting for you at the centre of gastronomy of Jingan district.
我们在静安区美食中心等你来。
